## Why This Is Asked
This tests end-to-end real-time monocular 3D pose with online calibration under non-ideal lighting and occlusions, plus efficient 3-shot adaptation.

## Key Concepts
- Monocular 3D pose under occlusion
- Online camera self-calibration
- Differentiable rendering with photometric losses
- Meta-learning for test-time adaptation
- Edge-GPU real-time constraints

## Code Example
```javascript
function forward(frame, state){
  const [detections, poses] = detector(frame);
  const extrinsics = state.update(detections, poses);
  const losses = photometricLoss(frame, detections, poses, extrinsics);
  return {losses, extrinsics};
}
```

